#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2018-09-03-replacing-gcm-in-tutanota.md
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Tutanota apps are Libre software, and we wanted to [publish our Android app on F-Droid](https://tutanota.com/blog/posts/open-source-email). We wanted our users to be able to use Tutanota on every ROM and every device, without the control of a third-party like Google. We decided to take on the challenge and to build our own push notification service."
