msgid "F-Droid is 10 years old, so this release also focused on modernizing.  Software developed and used over 10 years inevitably builds up cruft and technical debt.  We took this opportunity to remove lots of things that were broken, unused, or unmaintained. So there are some breaking changes, as detailed in the Changelog.  We hope this all makes it a lot easier for new contributors to get involved and make valuable contributions, all while making things work better for existing contributors."
